data.description: 55K price improvement since the original list price for greater market competitiveness and for you to celebrate the New Year in your new home. Discover 4177 Diamond Dr in Diamond Springs, a remarkable 3-bed, 2.5-bath single-family residence on a vast 23522 sq ft lot. This home offers a spacious 2352 sq ft of living area, underlined by potential and opportunity. Included are 675 sq ft of vinyl flooring and 80 sq ft of mosaic tile, along with a new toilet, setting the stage for a personalized renovation. The property features a wheelchair-accessible landscaped front yard and a private, fenced backyard. The propane-equipped kitchen awaits your culinary creativity. Conveniently located near essential amenities, this home is perfect for investors or DIY enthusiasts looking to make their mark. The expansive 750 sq ft lower level offers immense potential for conversion, possibly into a rental unit or extra living space. Ample room for ADU development enhances its appeal. Outdoor imagery includes grass enhancements to showcase possibilities. Seize the chance to transform 4177 Diamond Dr into your dream home or a lucrative investment in the charming Diamond Springs community.
